    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>All-white cotton coverlets with distinctive geometric designs in weft loop weave. Originally made in Bolton, England, and copied in North America.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
